Package server.Model

package server.Model
  • Class
    Description
    CommonGoal
    This Class represents the single CommonGoal card as written in the game rules.
    GameBoard
    This Class resembles the actual structure of the game with all its components.
    GameModel
    This Class contains all the components of the Model of the Game.
    ItemBag
    This Class represents the ItemBag as described in the game rules.
    ItemTile
    This abstract Class represents a generic single ItemTile in the LivingRoom.
    LivingRoom
    This Class represents the LivingRoom as described in the Game Rules.
    NullItemTile
    This Class represents a single ItemTile in the LivingRoom that is not available to be picked or moved but has the only purpose of completing the structure of the LivingRoom at its boards.
    PersonalGoal
    This Class represents the single PersonalGoal card as written in the game rules.
    PlayableItemTile
    This Class represents a single ItemTile in the LivingRoom, that is available to be picked or moved but under specific conditions.
    Player
    This Class represents a Player in the current game.
    Shelf
    This Class represents the Shelf of a single Player as described in the game rules.
    SimpleGameModel
    SimpleGameModel is the immutable copy of GameModel which is provided to the RemoteClient through TurnView.
    SimpleLivingRoom
    SimpleLivingRoom is the immutable copy of LivingRoom which is provided to the RemoteClient through TurnView.
    SimplePlayer
    SimplePlayer is the immutable copy of Player which is provided to the RemoteClient through TurnView.
    SimpleShelf
    SimpleShelf is the immutable copy of Shelf which is provided to the RemoteClient through TurnView.
